org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.ppc

Class MIR_Ternary

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.InstructionFormat
      • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.ppc.ArchInstructionFormat
        • org.jikesrvm.compilers.opt.ir.ppc.MIR_Ternary

  • public final class MIR_Ternary
extends ArchInstructionFormat
    The MIR_Ternary InstructionFormat class. The header comment for Instruction contains an explanation of the role of InstructionFormats in the opt compiler's IR.
